Code Formatting On Mac:
    Shift + Option + F

Code Folding On Mac:
    Command+ Option + [

Copy Line Up/Down On Mac: 
    Shift + Option + Up/Down

Split Editor
    On Mac: Command + \ or 2,3,4

Select Word
On Mac: Command + Shift + Right arrow / Left arrow

Opening and Closing the Sidebar
    On Mac: Command + b
ls
Navigate to a Specific Line
    On Mac: Ctrl + g or Ctrl + p

Delete Previous Word
    On Mac: Command + delete

Select in Words
On Mac: Command + Shift + Right arrow / Left arrow

Deleting a Line
    On Mac: Command + x

Add Cursor Above/Below
    On Mac: Command + Alt + upArrow / downArrow

